  [QA] Revision bump to 0.3.12_p5-r2. EAPI 5, sorted dependencies, added missing
  gdk-pixbuf:2 dependency as /usr/bin/graveman needs libgdk_pixbuf-2.0.so.0,
  replaced deprecated G2CONF by gnome2_src_configure, src_unpack -->
  src_prepare.

